data.description: GOLF COURSE HOME WITH A ( 4 ) CAR GARAGE, AND SITTING ON ( .53 ) OF AN ACRE OF PROPERTY!!! Located in The Valle Vista Golf Course Community is this 4 Bedroom / 2 Bath home being 1,944 Sqft in size, and is sitting on ( .53 ) of an Acre of Property on a corner lot! 2 Garages with 1 detached, and the other is attached to the home fitting 4 cars total, or can make one of them a workshop! Plenty of storage! Also there is a Carport for extra shaded parking! Plenty of space with Beautiful Views of the Golf Course, and Open Land across the street! Inside has a good size Kitchen with plenty of Cabinet space! Living Room features a wood Ship Lap Ceiling, and a Wood Burning Stove! Master Bedroom is a good size with access into the backyard! Master Bathroom features the His & Hers Sinks, Walk In Closet, and Walk In Shower! All 3 spare Bedrooms are all roughly the same good size! Newer A/C and Heating Unit! Newer Water Heater! Back and Front Yard are both Fully Landscaped! Lots of space for all your needs! Valle Vista has to offer the 18 hole Golf Course, Pool, Park, Playground, Restaurant, Clubhouse, Bar, Pro Shop, Big Belly Nellies, and more! Come cruise on by, and check out the curb appeal anytime...
